# üé® Viral Carousel Generator (AI Design Engine)

**Architected by Smit Godiyal**

An automated content engine that turns a single topic into a professionally designed, 5-slide LinkedIn/Instagram carousel in seconds. It combines **Generative AI** for viral hook writing with **Python Image Processing** for pixel-perfect design.

